      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form assumptions (turbulence model, hemolysis power-law exponents) documented with literature justification.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST and Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model selected based on published literature for centrifugal blood pumps. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2; selection rationale documented."
