      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters (viscosity, density, hematocrit) documented with nominal values and sources.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties set to bovine blood at 37°C per FDA benchmark protocol. Hematocrit 33%. All inputs documented in the simulation report. Formal input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Number of experimental replicates and sample preparation protocol documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark provides triplicate measurements at each operating point with documented blood preparation protocol. Formal statistical power analysis of test samples not required at MRL 2; available replication noted."
    },
